References: <C819AF41.4253%g-feng@northwestern.edu>
Message-ID: <4BF44C9B.1060403@fhcrc.org>

Hi Gilbert,

It sounds like you want to see the manual page for the toggleProbes()
function.  By default, multple mapping probes are not exposed.  But they
ARE in the db and you CAN expose then by using toggleProbes().


  Marc


